reviewText: When I tried to remove the "Spitfire birth of a legend" DVD from the DVD case, it broke.  I am now trying to see if I can get a replacement.
A Christmas gift to my boyfriend, and one of the few DVD sets on the subject he does not already own.  He looked thrilled after he opened it and saw what it was.  :)
Bought this for my Dad for Father's Day. He loved it!
This was a gift for my son.  I haven't watched it, but he is quite satisfied with it... Good video...
